# Music Folder Configuration
# 
# To connect your music playlist folder:
# 1. Copy this file and rename it to: music_config.txt
# 2. Edit music_config.txt and add your music folder path below
# 3. Restart the application
#
# Example paths:
# Windows: C:\Users\YourName\Music\MyPlaylist
# Or: D:\Music\Songs
#
# The system will scan all subfolders and find all audio files
# Supported formats: .mp3, .wav, .flac, .ogg, .m4a, .wma, .aac
#
# Your music folder path (remove the # and add your path):
# C:\Users\hp\Music
